fields.comment: Such a cute lil plant baby!
Was really de-hydrated when it arrived. Not sure it'll survive the year.
Colour looked brighter on the website but otherwise it's in a really good condition
Quite a temperamental plant! Kind of wish I'd gone for something a little easier to look after
This was the perfect plant pick for me - I'm often away for work but luckily it only needs watering about once every two weeks
Bought this for my sister and she's given it pride of place on her mantlepiece - that's a stamp of approval!
Made the mistake of placing this plant in direct sunlight and it lost its vibrant colour a little. Have moved into a shadier spot so hoping it gets better
Leaves were damaged when it arrived
I've received multiple compliments on this since popping it on my office desk! Might even buy another for my kitchen at home!
Was worried my room would be a bit dark but so far this thing is THRIVING!
OMG this little fellow honestly brightens my day! I'm so happy with my purchase - thank you!
So great to know it's cat-friendly and adds some colour to my living room
